Here is the list of sign recognition files or PDFs that I have been reading, collecting, or using as part of my research and exploration. These materials cover various aspects of sign recognition, including theory, implementation, datasets, and practical applications.
- https://ijisae.org/index.php/IJISAE/article/view/5667/4406
- http://github.com/AlvaroCavalcante/hand-face-detectorç
- https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/alvarole/hand-and-face-detection-focused-on-sign-language?resource=download
